column2: Give me all ESA astronauts.
column3:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> 
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> 
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> 
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri 
WHERE { 
        ?uri rdf:type dbo:Astronaut . 
        ?uri dbo:type res:European_Space_Agency .
}

column2: Who is the youngest Pulitzer Prize winner?
column3:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> 
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> 
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> 
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri
WHERE { 
        ?uri dbo:award res:Pulitzer_Prize .
        ?uri dbo:birthDate ?d .
} 
ORDER BY DESC(?d)
OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

column2: Which frequent flyer program has the most airlines?
column3:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> 
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> 
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> 
PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> 	
SELECT ?uri 
WHERE { 
         ?airline rdf:type dbo:Airline. 
         ?airline dbp:frequentFlyer ?uri.
         ?uri rdf:type yago:FrequentFlyerPrograms.

}
ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(DISTINCT ?airline))
OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

column2: Which of the volcanoes that erupted in 1550 is still active?

PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri 
WHERE {
        ?uri rdf:type dbo:Volcano . 
        ?uri dbo:eruptionYear ?y .
        FILTER (year(?y) = 1550)
        ?uri text:"is" text:"active" . 
}
